children.subject: It is also good to know that the course has been updated quite a bit since the archived webcasts. They are no longer representative of what the course is like. Machine learning is a rapidly advancing field, and consequently, the course material (even those parts that are introductory) adapts to make sure that students' understanding is centered in a way that will serve them for the long run.

The link for fall 2017 is not correct, that points to summer 2018.

The link for fall 2017 should be http://fa17.eecs189.org/

Likewise for spring 2018 it should be http://sp18.eecs189.org/
